Tun daga wannan yammacin ne shugaban Amurka Donald Trump zai fara jerin gangamin da za a yi a birnin Willing da ke jihar West Virginia.
Wannan taron yana daya daga cikin biyar da aka shirya, ciki har da wuraren zaman lafiya kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Bayan da aka jinkirta tabbatar da rinjaye a kotun koli, Trump ya nemi taimako daga zaben da za a yi a cikin watan Nuwamba, saboda jam'iyyar Republican ta yanke shawarar rasa rinjaye a majalisa idan an jinkirta zaben.
A wane lokaci kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia?
An ce taron zai gudana a karfe 7 na yamma a ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018, a tashar Iti Tunnayt.
Za ku kuma iya kallon taron Trump a yammacin Virginia ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen kai tsaye a kan layi ta hanyar danna maɓallin da ke ƙasa.
Wataƙila shugaban ya tilasta wa Bretta Kavano, wanda ke zaune a Kotun Koli, don ya yi fushi da zargin da ake yi masa na lalata; saboda haka, an kira shi zuwa makon daya bayan zaben a majalisar dattijai don tabbatar da hukuncin da za a yi, yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban batun waɗannan taron shine don taimakawa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar gwaji mai tsanani a zaben Nuwamba.
Don haka, taron gangamin Trump na mako mai zuwa zai taimaka wajen ƙarfafa masu sa kai da masu goyon baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke ƙoƙarin haɓaka da kuma kare jam'iyyarsu tare da mutane a majalisar wakilai da majalisar dattijai, kamar yadda aka bayyana a kan Reuters.
