HIV da AIDS: Kasar Sin ta ce yawan masu kamuwa da cutar ya karu da kashi 14%
Kasar Sin ta bayar da rahoton cewa yawan kamuwa da cutar a tsakanin mutanen da ke fama da cutar HIV da AIDS ya karu da kashi 14%.
A cewar jami'an kiwon lafiya, mutane fiye da 820,000 ne ke fama da cutar a kasar.
A cikin rabin rabin 2018, an gano kusan sababbin lokuta 40,000.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka na kamuwa da cututtuka sun kasance ta hanyar jima'i, saboda sun kasance a baya.
A wasu wurare a kasar Sin, an yi al'ada cewa mutane suna kamuwa da cutar HIV saboda zubar da jini.
Amma a yanzu ba za a iya cewa babu adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ba, in ji jami'an lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taron da aka gudanar a lardin Yunnan.
A cikin shekara guda, adadin mutanen da ke fama da cutar HIV da AIDS ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Kwayar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i ita ce babbar matsalar al'ummar LGBT a kasar Sin.
An halatta jima'i tsakanin maza da mata a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma ana ganin yana da mummunar tasiri ga al'ummar LGBT.
Saboda dabi'u masu ra'ayin mazan jiya a kasar, a cikin 70-90% na bayanan da aka sani, maza na LGBTI sun karbi matan aure.
Wannan cuta tana faruwa ne saboda rashin kariya ta jima'i.
Don taimakawa wannan, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin bunkasa samar da maganin rigakafin cutar HIV tun daga shekara ta 2003.
