Rashin shirin samarwa ya kasance mai mahimmanci, saboda jiragen ruwa na Baden Vürtemberg sun bukaci kimanin mutane 120 a cikin kwamiti, wanda shine kawai rabin yawan ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa na tsohon Bremen.
