Ofishin jakadancin tarayya na New York yana neman hukuncin kisa ga Saipov, wanda ake zargi da kisan mutane takwas a New York - wanda ba a yi amfani da shi ba a jihar tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekaru 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari kan hanyar keke a kan titin West-Side a Lower Manhattan, inda ya buge masu tafiya da masu hawan keke.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya haifar da mummunan rauni ga jiki, a cikin niyyar neman hukuncin kisa a gundumar Kudu ta New York.
Bisa ga takardun kotu, hukuncin kisa zai yiwu a kan waɗannan matakai biyu.
Bayan makonni bayan harin, babban kotun tarayya ta rubuta Saipov da laifin 22 wanda ya hada da kisan kai guda takwas, cin zarafi, lalata mota, wanda yawanci ake amfani da shi a cikin aikin aikata laifuka na tarayya.
